            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿آيَةً﴾ عَلاَمَةً عَلَى تَحَقُّقِ مَا بَشَّرَتْنِي بِهِ المَلاَئِكَةُ.</p>\n<h2>﴿سَوِيًّا﴾ صَحِيحًا، مُعَافًى.</h2>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "19:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿الْمِحْرَابِ﴾ المُصَلَّى الَّذِي يُتَعَبَّدُ فِيهِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فَأَوْحَى إِلَيْهِمْ﴾ أَشَارَ إِلَيْهِمْ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿بُكْرَةً وَعَشِيًّا﴾ صَبَاحًا، وَمَسَاءً.</h2>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "19:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿خُذِ الْكِتَابَ﴾ التَّوْرَاةَ.</h2>\n<p>﴿بِقُوَّةٍ﴾ بِجِدٍّ، وَاجْتِهَادٍ؛ حِفْظًا، وَفَهْمًا، وَعَمَلاً.</p>\n<h2>﴿الْحُكْمَ﴾ الحِكْمَةَ وَحُسْنَ الفَهْمِ وَالعَمَلِ.</h2>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "19:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَحَنَاناً﴾ رَحْمَةً وَمَحَبَّةً.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَزَكَاةً﴾ طَهَارَةً مِنَ الذُّنُوبِ وَبَرَكَةً.</h2>"
        },
